    "summary": "The user is experiencing side effects (nausea, tremors) after starting Lithium and asks for advice on managing them, including whether to increase water intake to \"flush it out.\" The assistant provides authoritative medical guidance, suggesting specific supplements like Vitamin B6 and Magnesium Citrate while correctly warning against excessive water intake causing hyponatremia and emphasizing the need for blood tests.",
